{"word":"G551 - ἀπείραστος - apeírastos - ap-i'-ras-tos - Not to be tempted","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπείραστος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apeírastos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-i'-ras-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Not to be tempted</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சோதிக்கப்படமுடியாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"untempted"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G3987 - πειράω - peiráō - pi-rah'-o/3987\">G3987</a>; <i>untried</i>, that is, <i>not temptable:</i> - not to be tempted.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1598/1598\">G1598</a>, <a href=\"#/G3984/3984\">G3984</a>, <a href=\"#/G3985/3985\">G3985</a>, <a href=\"#/G3986/3986\">G3986</a>, <a href=\"#/G3987/3987\">G3987</a>, <a href=\"#/G551/551\">G551</a>"}]}